name: Hiss
personality: timid with strangers but once he is comfortable with someone, he can remember the sound of their footsteps and will approach, mewing pathetically, hoping for pets.
likes: scratching the tires on motorbikes, sitting in puddles, splooting when he is feeling relaxed, being patted on his bum, scratching his ears on anyone's shoe
dislikes: the sound of plastic bags rustling terrifies him for some reason
other: lives happily in the carpark although he can also be found climbing on the covered walkways in the neighborhood. has cleverly trained himself to use drains as a toilet. although he usually pretends to be a starving orphan, actually he has a devoted carer who feeds him special food daily, plus he usually eats most of another cat's food too.
